flowchart TD
    Q[User query] --> T[Create request trace_id]
    T --> C[IntentClassifier<br/>DOC_QA ARTIFACT_SEARCH USER_SEARCH HYBRID OUT_OF_SCOPE]
    C --> O{Intent}
    O -->|OUT_OF_SCOPE| B[Bounded refusal response]
    O -->|USER_SEARCH| N[Name candidate resolution]
    N -->|Exact match| P[Fetch profile directly<br/>no generation required]
    N -->|Ambiguous| D[LLM disambiguation]
    N -->|No name hit| R1[Semantic user-profile retrieval]
    O -->|DOC_QA| R2[Retrieve platform_docs]
    O -->|ARTIFACT_SEARCH| R3[Retrieve artifact_summaries]
    O -->|HYBRID| R4[Retrieve docs + artifacts + users]
    C --> W[QueryRewriter<br/>optimize retrieval query]
    W --> R1
    W --> R2
    W --> R3
    W --> R4
    R1 --> PB[Intent-specific prompt builder]
    R2 --> PB
    R3 --> PB
    R4 --> PB
    PB --> G[Generate via LiteLLM]
    G --> F[Format answer<br/>artifacts users sources trace_id]
    P --> F
    D --> F
    B --> F
    F --> E[Return response to UI]
    F --> L1[Layer 1 heuristic scores]
    F --> L2[Layer 2 background eval]
    L1 --> LF[Langfuse trace]
    L2 --> LF
